I recently came across this beautiful Mother’s Day video by @clinicplusindia and it got me thinking! As mothers all we want is to make our angels strong, maybe even stronger than ourselves. And true strength comes from within. And that is exactly what I do for Ahana. I keep reminding her that she is stronger than she thinks. I want her to be ready to face the world head on! I can truly say - Meri Beti Strong! 

So this Mother’s Day, share this video with the strong ladies around you and remind them that there is nothing they can’t do!
